# WAI-Harness — v4 restore-safe tracking model (redressed S134)
#
# RESTORE-COMPLETENESS INVARIANT: a spoke MUST be fully reconstructible from
# (git remote) + (basher managed restore) alone. Therefore every NON-regenerable
# artifact lives in git: WAI-State.json, lugs/, WAI-LugIndex.jsonl, initiatives/
# (incl. savepoints), signals/, pathgraph/, teachings/.
# Only DERIVED / regenerable runtime is ignored (a tool re-creates it; never source).
# managed/ stays tracked + MANIFEST-verified (integrity checks are managed-scoped,
# so tracking local/ does not affect harness integrity/parity/upgrade verification).
#
# SUPERSEDES the prior blanket `spoke/local/** + hub/local/**` ignore, which made the
# spoke's work-state unrestorable (empty brain after clone + basher restore).

# --- regenerable runtime (re-created by a tool; never source of truth) ---
**/runtime/
**/.autosave/
**/*-brief.json
**/.activated
# session track history is telemetry (harvested by track-collector), not operational
# state needed to restore-and-run; WAI-State.json holds the live session pointer.
**/spoke/local/sessions/
**/hub/local/sessions/

# advisor-derived scans / reports / queues (regenerated every run)
**/advisors/*/scan_state.json
**/advisors/*/scan_history.jsonl
**/advisors/*/passes.jsonl
**/advisors/*/vectors.jsonl
**/advisors/*/findings-log.jsonl
**/advisors/*/reports/
**/advisors/octo/council_directives.json
**/advisors/octo/hub_work_queue.json
**/advisors/quartermaster/inventory.json
**/octo/job-queue.jsonl
**/octo/spoke-summaries/
**/autopilot/wheel-activity.html
**/autopilot/runs.jsonl
# regenerable queues / indexes (rebuilt from lugs + initiatives)
**/findings-log.jsonl
**/schedule-index.json
**/ready-queue.json
# NOTE: advisor CONFIG is durable + tracked (feeds.yaml, context_prompt.md, definitions);
# only the per-advisor scan_state/passes/vectors/findings/reports caches are ignored.

# --- build / OS / secrets (never source) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.DS_Store
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/.provider
